data.description: Immerse yourself in the serene symphony of nature, where the gentle rustle of evergreen trees, the crisp scent of fresh air, and the mesmerizing spectacle of starlit skies await. Tucked away on a secluded corner lot, this meticulously maintained property offers an oasis of tranquility. NEW Roof, NEW Septic System and a Newer 40-gallon hot water heater, alongside a newer well, this home is primed for comfortable living. Its open floor plan and split bedroom design facilitate effortless everyday life, while soaring ceilings and expansive windows invite natural light to dance throughout the interior. Step onto the 12x12 deck or peer through the dining room window to witness the captivating ballet of hummingbirds, jays, squirrels, and deer that frequent the surroundings. With an oversized garage to accommodate all your recreational gear and a spacious shed for property maintenance tools, this home ensures ample storage for all your needs. Situated just down the road from 33,000 acres of BLM land and less than an hour away from an array of water sports along the Arkansas River, the Royal Gorge, Salida, Westcliffe, and Canon City, adventure awaits at your doorstep. Whether you prefer to hike, fish, hunt, ski, or simply unwind in the embrace of nature, this property offers endless possibilities for country mountain living, leisure and relaxation.
